Incredible images of cervical cancer cells won Markus Posch, from the Centre for Gene Regulation and Expression at Dundee University, the award of regional winner in the microscopy section.

Eric Roman, General Manager of Research and Applied Markets, GE Healthcare Life Sciences, said: 'This year’s winning images are as beautiful and compelling as ever. 

